## Installation

Try it live on [itch.io](https://ceccopierangiolieugenio.itch.io/dumb-paint-tool)

or install it from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/dumbPaintTool):

```bash
pip install dumbPaintTool --upgrade

dumbPaintTool
```
